<div><head>棋品一卷</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.2">序曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.3">弈之時義大矣哉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.4">體希徵之趣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.5">含奇正之情，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.6">靜則合道，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.7">動必適變。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.8">若夫入神造極之靈，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.9">經武緯文之德，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.10">故可與和樂等妙，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.11">上藝齊工。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.12">支公以為手談，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.13">王生謂之坐隱，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.14">是以漢魏名賢高品間出，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.15">晉宋盛士逸思爭流，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.16">雖復理生於數研，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.17">求之所不能。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.18">涉義出乎幾爻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.19">彖未之或盡。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.20">聖上聽朝之餘，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.21">因日之暇，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.22">逈景紆情，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.23">降臨小道，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.24">以為凝神之性，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.25">難限入玄之致不窮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.26">令撰錄名氏隨品詳書，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.27">俾粹理深情，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-1a.28">永垂於來葉。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.2">江霦與土恢等，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.3">棋第一品，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.4">道第五品。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.5">羊玄保為黃門侍郎，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.6">善奕，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.7">棋品第三。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.8">宋文帝亦好奕，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.9">與賭郡。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.10">玄保戲勝以補。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.11">宣城太守常中使至，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.12">玄保曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.13">「今日上何召我耶？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.14">其子戌曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.15">「金溝清泚銅池，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.16">搖颺既佳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-2a.17">風景當得劇棊。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.2">到溉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.3">奕棋人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.4">第六品，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.5">與朱异韋黯於御座，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.6">校棋、比勢、覆局不差一道。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.7">陸雲公大同，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.8">未受武帝詔校定棊品。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.9">到溉、朱异下並集雲公。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.10">瓊年八歲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.11">於客前覆局，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.12">由是都下號曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.13">「神童」。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.14">异言之于武帝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.15">召見，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.16">風神警亮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.17">進退詳審，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1662_CHANT_001-3a.18">帝甚異之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
